T1  - The valuation of American options on bonds1Earlier versions of this paper have been presented at the European Finance Association meeting in Rotterdam, at the Financial Options Research Centre, Warwick University, and at the Hong Kong University of Science and Technology. We thank Anurag Gupta for able research assistance. We would also like to thank an anonymous referee for detailed comments on an earlier draft of the paper.1
AU  - Ho, T.S.
